<topic id="open-find-resource-dialog">
  <title>Open/Find Resource Dialog Box</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Searching documents<indexterm>Open/Find Resource dialog
          box</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Open/Find Resource dialog box</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p id="p_xyt_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> dialog box offers advanced search capabilities.
      To open the dialog box, go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Find</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol> Open/Find Resource (<shortcut
            conkeyref="reusable-oxygen-shortcuts-list/ctrl_shift_r_shortcut"/>)</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>. You can also click the <uicontrol><image href="../img/OpenResource16.png"
          id="image_k5h_gkp_sr"/>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> toolbar button or use the
          <uicontrol><image href="../img/OpenResource16.png" id="image_pwl_jnp_sr"/>Search for
        file</uicontrol> action that is available in some URL input fields.</p>
    <p id="p_yyt_bgk_54b">
      <fig id="fig_zyt_bgk_54b">
        <title>Open/Find Resource Dialog Box</title>
        <image href="../img/sa_open_find_resource.png"/>
      </fig>
    </p>
    <p id="p_azt_bgk_54b">You can use this dialog box to find a file in the current <ph
        keyref="product"/> project <ph product="editor author">or in one of the <xref
          keyref="glossentry_ditamap"><term>DITA maps</term></xref> opened in <xref
          keyref="dita_edit-maps" format="dita">the <uicontrol>DITA Maps Manager</uicontrol>
          view</xref>
      </ph> by typing a few letters of the file name or a fragment of the content you are searching
      for. The <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> dialog box also supports searching in
      document edits (comments, tracked change insertions/deletions, and highlighted content).</p>
    <section conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/search-results-section" id="d2e82"/>
    <section id="options_available_in_the_dialog_box">
      <title>Options Available in the Dialog Box</title>
      <p id="p_czt_bgk_54b">The <uicontrol>Open/Find Resource</uicontrol> dialog box includes the following options:<ul
          id="ul_xnp_kdn_1p">
          <li id="li_dzt_bgk_54b"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/in-file-paths"
              product="author developer editor"/></li>
          <li id="li_ezt_bgk_54b"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/in-content"
              product="author developer editor"/></li>
          <li id="li_fzt_bgk_54b"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/in-reviews"
              product="author developer editor"/></li>
          <li id="li_gzt_bgk_54b"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/options" product="author developer editor"
            /></li>
          <li id="li_hzt_bgk_54b"><ph id="clear-index"><uicontrol>Clear Index</uicontrol> - Clears the index.</ph></li>
          <li id="li_izt_bgk_54b"><ph conkeyref="reusables-editing-documents/reindex"/></li>
        </ul></p>
    </section>
